1753Sekkhaṃ dhammaṃ saṃsaṭṭho sekkho dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā—  sekkhaṃ ekaṃ khandhaṃ saṃsaṭṭhā tayo khandhā…pe…  dve khandhe…pe… . (1)
